name: Material Hub
description: A modern theme for Github. Google's Material Design was kept in mind for most of the project. In this design I tried to put their current content in a fresh and modern look without altering the workflow. Customizations -Primary Color -Primary Hover Color -Dark Mode (Beta) Github: https://github.com/MrRobotjs/Material-Hub =================== This style is still a work in progress, it will be continuously getting updates. The style will be finished over time but until then If you find something that I have missed, please let me know! =================== Your feedback and rating towards the style is highly appreciated! Check out more of my styles here.

discussions.name: Thanks for dark mode option. Few weird quirks with the hover+show nav bar, but still works great
